                  </persName>
            . I am an extra constable. On the 14th of April, about twelve o'clock, as I got into Cheapside, I saw the prisoner and the last witness of this side of the Old Change; the prisoner was endeavouring to get away from him, they separated, the prisoner stopped to pick up his hat; I secured him.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I am innocent.</p>
